Subject: The $500 bus

Generally, the $500 bus today comes without an engine and pretty rough. 
Here's a summary of the $500 buses listed o page 1 of www.thesamba.com:

Price          Engine          Location
500             poor engine   Norfolk, Va.
250              no engine     Gainsville, Fl
900              UM               Melbourne, Fl 
250              no engine       Gainsville, Fl
500               no engine      SF, Ca
50                shell              Steger, Il

